{"tid":1148473,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你會揀日本定韓國","createTime":"2019-05-10T13:10:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T07:31:32.000Z","uid":43178,"like":51,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c30b4204a7245c561b0cd21438f275ffb9753dd7","tid":1148473,"uid":43178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:10:29.000Z","msg":"俾你去永住/歸化去日本/韓國<br />\n你會揀？<br />\n正皮 日本<br />\n負皮 韓國"},{"pid":"f97574e3e24e986bdb784341fcf8a54e0d4114a4","tid":1148473,"uid":191650,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:16:43.000Z","msg":"梗係日本啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddc0b92b33c61a65cf84cb743a67cd5ebbc7567a","tid":1148473,"uid":113373,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:38:51.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">反對修訂逃犯條例 香港的終局之戰</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">立法會集會:<br />\n5月11日 星期六 早上8:30 (開會討論修訂逃犯條例)<br />\n<br />\n若不能阻止立法，稍後立法會二讀/三讀時，行動將升級<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n事態危急<br />\n一定要阻止立法<br />\n否則香港直送中國受審<br />\n到時中國話你犯咗中國法律 無需證據 無需理由<br />\n就可以光明正大係香港夾你返中國 <br />\n坐黑獄 洗你腦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">此修例禍害大於23條立法<br />\n23條&gt;&gt;&gt;(需危害國家安全，香港審判，香港監禁)<br />\n<br />\n修訂逃犯條例 &gt;&gt;&gt;(莫需有，中國政府可任意控告香港人多達46條罪行，香港會配合執法將你拘捕，移交中國審判及監禁，無需證據 無需理由)</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"cf7d79363fe009706ab979711cb507b6d50f950f","tid":1148473,"uid":232594,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:52:12.000Z","msg":"去韓國同番大陸有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f292fac446e6908a2782523f5cb193e4b76c4a48","tid":1148473,"uid":194398,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-10T13:58:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2a1e439cf430a3a11422002d8039b5ae8b85b1fb","tid":1148473,"uid":43178,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"f292fac446e6908a2782523f5cb19